\/","url_meta":{"origin":35811,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Vice: Evil within people lies in greed and cowardice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe worst evil within a man is his restless greed and his utmost cowardice.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2511 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21704,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/21\/beware-greed-miserliness\/","url_meta":{"origin":35811,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Greed: Beware of greed, miserliness, wickedness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of greed, for it was only greed that destroyed those before you. It commanded them to be miserly, and they did so. It commanded them to sever their family ties, and they did so.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category